OL,3,CBadenoch: 'Disappointing' it took ITV
OL,4,Cdrama to prioritise Post Office
OL,5,Cpayments
OL,7,FThe Tory leader said Monday that ITV's
OL,8,FPost Office drama "brought the urgency
OL,9,Fand raised the prioritisation" of Post
OL,10,FOffice payouts.
OL,12,FSpeaking at the Horizon IT inquiry,
OL,13,FKemi Badenoch said it is "extremely
OL,14,Fdisappointing" that it took the
OL,15,Fseries, released at the beginning of
OL,16,Fthis year, to change "the priority of
OL,17,Fthe issue".
OL,19,FThe government allowed "bureaucracy to
OL,20,Fget in the way of redress" for wronged
OL,21,Fsubpostmasters, she added.
