OL,7,FBadenoch claimed that, at the time,
OL,8,Fshe and ex-Postal Affairs Minister
OL,9,FKevin Hollinrake "wanted to get the
OL,10,Fmoney out there" but were "always
OL,11,Fgiven a reason why we couldn't" by
OL,12,Fgovernment officials.
