OL,3,CBadenoch: 'Disappointing' it took ITV
OL,4,Cdrama to prioritise Post Office
OL,5,Cpayments
OL,7,FExplaining why she felt bureaucracy
OL,8,Fwas getting in the way of redress,
OL,9,FBadenoch told the probe on Monday: "I
OL,10,Ffeel that there is often too much
OL,11,Fbureaucracy in the way of getting
OL,12,Fthings done, because people are
OL,13,Fworried about process.
OL,15,F"They are worried about: if things go
OL,16,Fwrong, they'll be on the hook for that.
OL,18,F"So they carry out lots of checks and
OL,19,Fbalances well beyond what I think is
OL,20,Frequired in order to deliver the right
OL,21,Foutcome."
