OL,7,FQuestioned by counsel to the inquiry,
OL,8,FJason Beer KC, on who allowed
OL,9,Fbureaucracy to get in the way of
OL,10,Fredress, Badenoch replied: "Well, the
OL,11,Fgovernment machine. I think I remember
OL,12,Fasking a question like: 'Why can't we
OL,13,Fjust give them the money?'"
