OL,4,Cdrama to prioritise Post Office
OL,5,Cpayments
OL,7,FLead campaigner and former
OL,8,Fsubpostmaster Sir Alan Bates
OL,9,Fpreviously told MPs he wanted the
OL,10,FDepartment for Business and Trade to
OL,11,Fset a deadline of March next year for
OL,12,Fredress payments for claimants who
OL,13,Ftook the Post Office to the High Court
OL,14,Fbetween 2017 and 2019.
OL,16,FAs of October 31, there were still 50
OL,17,Fvictim claims that had yet to be
OL,18,Fsettled.
