OL,3,CBadenoch: 'Disappointing' it took ITV
OL,4,Cdrama to prioritise Post Office
OL,5,Cpayments
OL,7,FParliament said last week it will
OL,8,Flaunch an inquiry looking at the
OL,9,Fdelays in compensation settlements,
OL,10,Fwith the Chair of the Business & Trade
OL,11,FSelect Committee, Liam Byrne MP
OL,12,Ftelling ITV News: "We on the committee
OL,13,Fare going to batter away at this, week
OL,14,Fin, week out, until it is job done.
OL,16,F"All of us on our committee are
OL,17,Ffrankly horrified and outraged by how
OL,18,Flong this has taken and we're just not
OL,19,Fgoing to give up."
